The evidence with the title 'Electing a black mayor leads to more black police officers ... ' says Oct 10, 2014  ... Ferguson , for example, is 67 percent black and has a police force of more than 50 officers , yet you can count its black police officers on one hand. Its mayor is white , as are five of its six City Council members.  ... Populations to be more likely to elect black mayors and more likely to have black police officers . 
